metadata.name: විශ්ව දේවතාව | Deity of Universe
metadata.description:
විශ්ව දේවතාව ( Vishwa Devathawa in  language " Sinhala" ) or  Deity of Universe. We believe the earth we walk on,  the Sun, the Moon, all the stars and all the planets were created by someone or something... we call them in many names Celestials, Gods , Deity, The Creator... 

This is the first of art of the collection to come..
